that your mom and dad

1109
00:57:39,549 --> 00:57:40,758
won't let you
just grow up

1110
00:57:40,842 --> 00:57:43,011
and be yourself,
be a woman.

1111
00:57:43,429 --> 00:57:45,347
Go with it.
Don't suppress
or deny it.

1112
00:57:45,431 --> 00:57:47,891
Use it in your life
and your work.

1113
00:57:49,645 --> 00:57:51,437
Okay. I mean...

1114
00:57:52,439 --> 00:57:55,441
That's... I'll have to
think about all that.

1115
00:57:56,694 --> 00:58:00,531
So, class is tomorrow
in Room 110, right?

1116
00:58:01,699 --> 00:58:03,868
No, it's been changed
to the theater.

1117
00:58:03,953 --> 00:58:05,912
I mean, what better place
for drama, right?

1118
00:58:05,996 --> 00:58:07,288
Yeah.

1119
00:58:09,166 --> 00:58:10,626
